{
  "stem": "4361.8",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 53,
      "text": "And then, like within two weeks, one morning, we look out the window, and we see someone on horseback, and it's Leonid.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 54,
      "text": "Somehow, he managed to come back, and he managed to get permission to marry this girl.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 55,
      "text": "But he said something.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 56,
      "text": "He said that I want you to know that life under the Communist regime is not what you know.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 57,
      "text": "And he described to me the life.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "As we now know, it was drab, uniform, no-- whatever, which didn't bother me.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But what I did was consult with my sister-in-law.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "What do I do?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And this is what she said to me.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "At that time, we did not yet have my older brother's knowledge of what happened to him because we were still waiting for him.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "She said to me like this, she said, Barbara, when your brother, [?",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Manot, ?] my husband, comes home, and he finds out that he lost his son, he lost his mother and father, and his-- and [?",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Shonie, ?] Alex, we've heard that he was in-- on the Danube.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "He was thrown into the Danube and his only living member of his family, his sister, his little sister is in Russia, how can I tell him that?",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "How can you do that?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And I did not go.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The sad part of it is that-- that soon thereafter, we found out about the end.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "This is when Dr.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Verner came home and told us what happened.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But very soon thereafter, I-- I-- I was devastated, devastated that-- that I lost-- now again, I lost everything.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I lost this man with whom I was in love and who was so good to me and who has showed me how to cry, and I don't have a brother.",
      "word_count": 31
    }
  ],
